cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper is about a deep generative model for image analysis and representation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The model also involves Bayesian inference (cs.AI) and deep learning (cs.NE), which are related sub-fields. Finally, the paper mentions implementation on graphical processor units (GPUs) for efficient large-scale learning, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM).
